                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I haven't encountered any items that have a DECENT spell damage increase AND good stats such as stamina/int.  Therefore I dont use them. I'd rather have higher int and stamina than the bonus. You can live longer with higher stamina and never have to use your mana shield.  This gives you more mana which = more damage (can spam spells more). Also, more INT = more chance to crit.
<br />

<br />
The content creators for armor and items in WoW have no concept what gear is uber and what gear isn't. I could take a full set of GREEN eagle gear and beat the living crap out of a mage with the full Magister's Mage Armor set in a duel.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
